Key Match Events: Shayan Jahangir scored 60 not out off 34 balls.
Dipendra Singh Airee took 3 wickets for 27 runs.
Aaron Jones was run out by Dipendra Singh Airee and Aasif Sheikh.
Monank Patel was bowled by Rijan Dhakal.
Saiteja Mukkamalla was caught by Rohit Paudel and bowled by Karan KC.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was held at Grand Prairie Cricket Stadium, Dallas.
USA won the toss and chose to field.
Nepal's Dipendra Singh Airee was a standout performer with both bat and ball.
The umpires for the match were Vijaya Mallela and Aditya Gajjar, both from the USA.
The match referee was Dean Cosker from England.
